Text: ...Andy Capp. A comic strip written by Limeys for American reading, converted to Mexican press. Boy, will this be the most classic case of "lost in translation" since technical reference manuals started shipping with parts made in China or what?
Magnifico. ¡¡Gracias!!. He tenido excelentes amigos Cockneys. Y estan topicamente caricaturizados pero con cariño. Recuerdan en mucho a los castizos.
